Title: Let 'Em Eat Cake
Plot: In the first season finale, George Sr. has a heart attack, and Maeby is jealous when George Michael likes another girl. Meanwhile, Lindsay decides to leave Tobias until a book he wrote a long time ago becomes a gay bestseller, and Buster and Annyong compete over women.
GuestStars: Ian Roberts, Judy Greer, Stacey Grenrock-Woods, Matt Walsh, Alessandra Toreson
